openslide
------------------------------------------
The OpenSlide library allows programs to access virtual slide files regardless
of the underlying image format.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.5-1
  libcairo-devel-1.18.4-1
  libcairo2-1.18.4-1
  libdicom-devel-1.2.0-1bl1
  libdicom1-1.2.0-1bl1
  libgdk_pixbuf2.0-devel-2.36.11-1
  libgdk_pixbuf2.0_0-2.36.11-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.87.0-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.87.0-1
  libjpeg-devel-3.1.2-1
  libjpeg8-3.1.2-1
  libopenjp2-devel-2.5.4-1
  libopenjp2_7-2.5.4-1
  libopenslide-devel-4.0.0-1bl2
  libopenslide1-4.0.0-1bl2
  libpng-devel-1.6.47-2
  libpng16-1.6.47-2
  libsqlite3-devel-3.49.1-1
  libsqlite3_0-3.49.1-1
  libtiff-devel-4.7.1-1
  libtiff7-4.7.1-1
  libxml2-2.10.4-2
  libxml2-devel-2.10.4-2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1
  zlib0-1.3.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cygport-0.37.4-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libcairo-devel-1.18.4-1
  libdicom-devel-1.2.0-1bl1
  libgdk_pixbuf2.0-devel-2.36.11-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.87.0-1
  libjpeg-devel-3.1.2-1
  libopenjp2-devel-2.5.4-1
  libpng-devel-1.6.47-2
  libsqlite3-devel-3.49.1-1
